# CameraSystem

## Purpose
Updates the orthographic camera each frame in response to keyboard, scroll, and window-resize input
events. Translation (WASD), zoom (scroll wheel), and aspect ratio (window resize) are applied only to
OrthographicCameraComponent entities where m_ReactsToInput = true. Camera matrix is rebuilt every
frame an event is present; skipped entirely when no relevant events arrived.

## Input Components
| Component | Access |
|---|---|
| KeyPressedEventComponent | read |
| MouseScrolledEventComponent | read |
| WindowResizeEventComponent | read |
| OrthographicCameraComponent | write |

## Output Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| OrthographicCameraComponent | write | Updates m_CameraPosition, m_ZoomLevel, m_AspectRatio, and the internal view-projection matrix |
